('ACC4761D', null, null, '"ACC37%:D"', 'null', 'Seminars in Accounting: Risk Management Technology', 'This course extends the basic concepts of enterprise risk management by focusing on the use of technology to facilitate the identification of key risk indicators and near misses. Through the use of hands-on laboratory sessions and case studies, the course will have a special emphasis on identifying key risk indicators and near misses on social media platforms such as Facebook, Twitter and blogs. The analysis of sentiments on these platforms will be used to illustrate the link of these sentiments to the identification and prediction of key risk indicators and near misses.', 4);
